titleInfo.title: Highly oxidized diiron complexes: generation, spectroscopy, and stabilities

mods.abstract: Oxidation of the diferric complex [(LFeOFeL)-O-III-L-III] to the monoradical complex [(LFeOFeL center dot)-O-III-L-III](+) and the diradical complex [(LFeOFeL center dot)-Fe-center dot-O-III-L-III](2+) is followed by a decay into monomeric complexes including a highly reactive putative [LFeIV=O] complex.
